{"title":"[正則表達式](一) ","date":"2020-03-22T08:37:35.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 22, 2020","L":"03/22/2020","MM-DD":"03-22"},"link":"2020/03/22/RegExp-1","tags":["JS","W3HEXSCHOOL"],"updated":"2020-03-22T11:58:28.379Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><h1>淺談正則表達式 (一)</h1>\n<p><strong>用途</strong>：用於制定字串間的規則，將其用於過濾字串上</p>\n<h2 id=\"建立表達式\">建立表達式</h2>\n<p>表達式的建立一般分成兩種方式，<font color=\"red\">變量</font>的宣告以及<font color=\"red\">物件</font>的宣告</p>\n<ul>\n<li>物件的宣告方式</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">RegExp</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"正則表達式\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"匹配模式\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>變量的宣告方式</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> banana=<span class=\"regexp\">/正則表達式/</span>匹配模式<span class=\"comment\">//變數寫法</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>傳入的參數主要有 <font color=\"blue\">正則表達式</font>以及<font color=\"blue\">匹配模式</font>兩種</p>\n<h2 id=\"test-的使用\">test()的使用</h2>\n<p>使用這個方法可以檢查一個字串是否符合表達式規則</p>\n<p>符合的話，返回true，否則返回false</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">RegExp</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"a\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =apple.test(<span class=\"string\">\"a\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =apple.test(<span class=\"string\">\"abcd\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"正則表達式\">正則表達式</h2>\n<p>正則表達式包含了<strong>字串規則</strong>+<strong>量詞</strong></p>\n<p><strong>量詞的使用</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>只對前一個內容起作用</li>\n<li>{n} :正好出現n次</li>\n<li>{m,n}:出現m到n次</li>\n<li>{m,}:出現m次以上</li>\n<li>+:至少一個 相當於{1,}</li>\n<li>*: 0個或多個  相當於{0,}</li>\n<li>? 0個或1個  相當於{0,1}</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ex:如果想要測試輸入的字串中<strong>是否包含</strong><font color=\"red\">\"a\"</font>這個字元</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">RegExp</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"a\"</span>)<span class=\"comment\">//method 1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple=<span class=\"regexp\">/a/</span> <span class=\"comment\">//method 2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =apple.test(<span class=\"string\">\"abcd\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>Ex:如果想要測試輸入的字串中是否包含<font color=\"red\">\"bbb\"</font>這個字元</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">RegExp</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"b{3}\"</span>)<span class=\"comment\">//method 1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple=<span class=\"regexp\">/b{3}/</span> <span class=\"comment\">//method 2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =apple.test(<span class=\"string\">\"abbbd\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>Ex:檢查字串中是否有<font color=\"red\">ababab</font> 存在</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> orange=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">RegExp</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"(ab){3}\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =orange.test(<span class=\"string\">\"abababhhh\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>Ex:檢查字串中是否有<font color=\"red\">a<font color=\"blue\">b</font>c </font>,<font color=\"red\">a<font color=\"blue\">bb</font>c </font>,<font color=\"red\">a<font color=\"blue\">bbb</font>c </font>   存在</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> orange=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">RegExp</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"ab{1,3}c\"</span>) </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =orange.test(<span class=\"string\">\"abcd\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"匹配模式\">匹配模式</h2>\n<p>主要有2個參數(順序可以顛倒)</p>\n<ul>\n<li><font color=\"red\">i</font>: ignore，忽略大小寫</li>\n<li><font color=\"red\">g</font>: 全局匹配模式</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ex: 檢查字串中是否有<strong>ab</strong>,<strong>Ab</strong>,<strong>aB</strong>,<strong>AB</strong>存在</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">RegExp</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"ab\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"i\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =apple.test(<span class=\"string\">\"abcd\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return true </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =apple.test(<span class=\"string\">\"aAb\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> result =apple.test(<span class=\"string\">\"aC\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//return false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>資料來源：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av74719082/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av74719082/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://ccckmit.wikidot.com/regularexpression\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://ccckmit.wikidot.com/regularexpression</a></li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>","next":{"title":"[演算法]馬可夫鏈 (Markov Chain)","link":"2020/03/08/MarkovChain"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/03/22/RegExp-1/"}